@startuml Admin_SkillsManagement

title Admin - Skills Management (Module C, E)

actor Admin as "🔐 Admin"

rectangle "SKILLS" {
    usecase "List All Skills" as SM1
    usecase "Create New Skill" as C13
    usecase "Update Skill" as SM2
    usecase "Delete Skill" as SM3
}

Admin --> SM1: 1. List skills
SM1 --> C13: 2. Create skill
SM1 --> SM2: 3. Update skill
SM1 --> SM3: 4. Delete skill

note right of SM1
  **Priority:** P1 (Important)
  **Status:** Need Validation
end note

@enduml
